Package gov.usgs.earthquake.quakeml

Class QuakemlPublicId

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.earthquake.quakeml.QuakemlPublicId
  • public class QuakemlPublicId
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility for generating Quakeml Public Ids. This mapping is used when converting EQXML or CUBE into Quakeml, and can parse IDs generated by this class. However, ANSS networks do not necesarily follow this convention when natively producing quakeml and so it should be used cautiously.
